<li id="cite_note-107"><b><a href="#cite_ref-107" title="">^</a></b> "He (Jesus) came to save all through means of Himself â all, I say, who through Him are born again to God and children, infants, and boys, and youths, and old men" (<a href="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/schaff/anf01.ix.iii.xxiii.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/schaff/anf01.ix.iii.xxiii.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Adversus Haereses</i>, ii, 22, 4</a>)</li>
